        "toolDescription": "This is the primary knowledge source for the Computer Science Department of Buriram Rajabhat University.\n\nFor any question related to:\n\n* admissions\n* curriculum\n* courses\n* teachers\n* staff\n* scholarships\n* activities\n* news\n* internships\n* cooperative education\n* contact information\n* university services\n\nyou MUST search this tool before generating an answer.\n\nNever answer these topics directly from model memory.\n\nIf the search result is empty or irrelevant, respond that the information was not found in the knowledge base.\n\nUse only retrieved content when answering.",
